_sText:
This is my first "texture" styled map.  It is on the larger side for a gungame map and provides both close-quarter indoors fighting and wide-open spaces outdoors.
There are also several high (really high) snipering spots and some hunker-down camping spots too (such as the texture car parking lot).

Watch your step on the spires - the fall won't kill you but the landing will.

~~~Worm
